Allows members with the correct rights to dismiss or change rank status of alliance members.

=== Forums F2 ===

Allows you to visit, post, rename, delete and create alliance forums.

=== Attacks F1 ===

Lists attacks against the alliance members (Provided that they have a Defense Minister).
